      "label": "rozwiązanie",
      "body": "\n\n<div class=\"switch_steps\">\n<div class=\"switch_step\">\n                Wszystkie punkty na osi \\(OX\\) mają wspólną cechę.\n                <div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    Ich współrzędna\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(x\\)-owa\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(y\\)-owa\n                    </div>\n                    jest równa \\(0\\).\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n                Podstawmy więc \\(y=0\\) do równania\n                \\[\n                (x + 2)² + (y + 3)² = 10\n                \\]\n                <div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    Otrzymamy \\((x+2)^2=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(7\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(1\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(5\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    A skoro \\((x+2)^2=1\\) to znaczy, że \\(x+2=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-1\\) lub \\(1\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(1\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-1\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n<div class=\"switch_line\">\n                    \\(x+2=-1\\) lub \\(x+2=1\\) oznacza, że \\(x=\\)\n                    <div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        &gt;&gt; wybierz &gt;&gt;\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(-3\\) lub \\(-1\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(1\\) lub \\(3\\)\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"switch_value\">\n                        \\(1\\) lub \\(-1\\)\n                    </div>\n                    .\n                    <div class=\"switch_show_next ks_button\">\n                        zatwierdź\n                    </div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"switch_step hidden\">\n                Punkty, w których okrąg \\((x + 2)² + (y + 3)² = 10\\) przecina oś \\(OX\\) to \\((-3,0)\\) i \\((-1,0)\\).\n                <div class=\"centered\">\n<img alt=\"punkty wspólne okręgu i osi OX\" src=\"static/okrag_os_ox.png\" width=\"400\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n"
    },
